                    "The era of lifetime employment at a single company is over. In 2026, career trajectories are fluid, and multiple roles are the norm, not the exception. What matters isn't how long you stayed, but what you learned, contributed, and how each experience prepared you for the next challenge. Frame your journey as intentional growth, and short stints become evidence of adaptability, not instability."
